{"tid":2266550,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"傳 馬明會係下年年頭 奪去靚湯既貞操？！","createTime":"2020-11-01T11:47:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-01T12:42:43.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4281ab28522406447c8b26325265d787a1ccc8cd","tid":2266550,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T11:47:37.000Z","msg":"【湯馬戀】傳馬國明向靚湯求婚成功　明年初娶湯洛雯外父送半億大屋<br />\n<br />\n男神馬國明與靚湯湯洛雯明年初結婚？今日（10月27日）有媒體爆料指，現年46歲的馬國明，與33歲湯洛雯雖然今年6月才拍拖，不過馬明已向靚湯求婚，並獲女方答應，傳二人將明年初結婚。<br />\n<br />\n而且有指TVB為兩人籌備婚禮，現在已暗中為二人聯絡贊助。另外，靚湯湯洛雯去年購入4,581萬元的馬鞍山雲海別墅中的Lily Avenue逾2,000呎別墅單位。<br />\n<br />\n雖然該物業的業主名是靚湯，不過據悉實際由她的父靚湯鎮宗出資購入，原計劃買入由湯家所住，現在湯父豪送予女兒作嫁妝。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2786523/%E3%80%90%E6%B9%AF%E9%A6%AC%E6%88%80%E3%80%91%E5%82%B3%E9%A6%AC%E5%9C%8B%E6%98%8E%E5%90%91%E9%9D%9A%E6%B9%AF%E6%B1%82%E5%A9%9A%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E3%80%80%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E5%88%9D%E5%A8%B6%E6%B9%AF%E6%B4%9B%E9%9B%AF%E5%A4%96%E7%88%B6%E9%80%81%E5%8D%8A%E5%84%84%E5%A4%A7%E5%B1%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2786523%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%25B9%25AF%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E6%2588%2580%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%2582%25B3%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2598%258E%25E5%2590%2591%25E9%259D%259A%25E6%25B9%25AF%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%25A9%259A%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%258A%259F%25E3%2580%2580%25E6%2598%258E%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2588%259D%25E5%25A8%25B6%25E6%25B9%25AF%25E6%25B4%259B%25E9%259B%25AF%25E5%25A4%2596%25E7%2588%25B6%25E9%2580%2581%25E5%258D%258A%25E5%2584%2584%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25B1%258B&d=Xh6WvVyDZ%2Fzj0BED8lYnh%2Bbr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=5ef60ea5\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2786523/%E3%80%90%E6%B9%AF%E9%A6%AC%E6%88%80%E3%80%91%E5%82%B3%E9%A6%AC%E5%9C%8B%E6%98%8E%E5%90%91%E9%9D%9A%E6%B9%AF%E6%B1%82%E5%A9%9A%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E3%80%80%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E5%88%9D%E5%A8%B6%E6%B9%AF%E6%B4%9B%E9%9B%AF%E5%A4%96%E7%88%B6%E9%80%81%E5%8D%8A%E5%84%84%E5%A4%A7%E5%B1%8B</a><br />\n<